{{Main|Football at the Tuvalu Games}}
The '''2014 Tuvalu Games men's football tournament''' is the 7th edition of Football at the 2014 [[Tuvalu Games]]. The tournament began on 3 May 2013 and finished on 31 May 2014.
All eight clubs participated. Defending champions were [[FC Tofaga]].

The winner [[FC Manu Laeva|Manu Laeva A]], who 2-0 won against [[FC Nanumaga|Ha'apai United A]].

